<p>
  You may wish to <a href="{{config.host.website}}/hosts">find another Fiscal Host</a> to apply to.</p>

  <p>You may also consider keeping the money in your own bank account instead of signing up with a Fiscal Host (<a href="https://docs.opencollective.com/help/fiscal-hosts/become-a-fiscal-host">more details</a>).
